Resume an interrupted optimization run

Usage: fastskill optimize resume [OPTIONS] <run-dir>

Arguments:
  <run-dir>  Path to the run directory to resume

Options:
      --skills-dir <skills-dir>  Override the skills directory path
      --global                   Use global skills directory (~/.config/fastskill/skills)
  -v, --verbose                  Enable verbose output
  -h, --help                     Print help
  -V, --version                  Print version

Syntax: optimize resume <run-dir>
